Lockheed Corp's Lockheed Missilesand Space Co Inc is being awarded a 304 mln dlr Air Forcecontract for work related to the Strategic Defense Initiative(SDI), the Defense Department said.    It said the work consists of a 34 month SDI BoostSurveillance and Tracking System demonstration/validationeffort which is expected to be completed in January 1990.    The department said 34.3 mln dlrs of the contract fundswill expire at the end of the current fiscal year. It addedthat 38 bids for the work were solicited and three proposalswere received. Reuter&#3;